		<section name="New project">
            <subsection name="Creation">
        		<div id="documentContent">
                <p>
                To create a new Maven project, go to File/New project.. menu item. Among other project types, there's the sample project template for maven as well.
                You will be prompted for artifactId, groupId, version etc. Clicking the Finish button will 
                create the project according to the template and your filled out values.
                </p>
